</style>

<a class="accessible-link u-tcYellow" href="/privacy" title="Privacy Policy">Privacy Policy</a>
<a class="accessible-link header--dropdown-link" href="https://www.academia.edu/login" title="Access your Academia.edu account">Log In</a>
<a class="accessible-link header--dropdown-link" href="https://www.academia.edu/signup" title="Sign Up">Sign Up</a>
...
```

Remember, this is a general guideline, and you should always test your website with accessibility tools and guidelines like WCAG (Web Content Accessibility Guidelines) to ensure compliance with all accessibility standards.

